Ta-seen tilka ayatu alqur-ani wakitabin mubeenin
Hudan wabushra lilmu/mineena
Allatheena yuqeemoona alssalata wayu/toona alzzakata wahum bial-akhirati hum yooqinoona
Inna allatheena la yu/minoona bial-akhirati zayyanna lahum a’malahum fahum ya’mahoona
Ola-ika allatheena lahum soo-o al’athabi wahum fee al-akhirati humu al-akhsaroona
Wa-innaka latulaqqa alqur-ana min ladun hakeemin ‘aleemin
Ith qala moosa li-ahlihi innee anastu naran saateekum minha bikhabarin aw ateekum bishihabin qabasin la’allakum tastaloona
Falamma jaaha noodiya an boorika man fee alnnari waman hawlaha wasubhana Allahi rabbi al’alameena
Ya moosa innahu ana Allahu al’azeezu alhakeemu
Waalqi ‘asaka falamma raaha tahtazzu kaannaha jannun walla mudbiran walam yu’aqqib ya moosa la takhaf innee la yakhafu ladayya almursaloona
Illa man thalama thumma baddala husnan ba’da soo-in fa-innee ghafoorun raheemun
Waadkhil yadaka fee jaybika takhruj baydaa min ghayri soo-in fee tis’i ayatin ila fir’awna waqawmihi innahum kanoo qawman fasiqeena
Falamma jaat-hum ayatuna mubsiratan qaloo hatha sihrun mubeenun
Wajahadoo biha waistayqanat-ha anfusuhum thulman wa’uluwwan faonthur kayfa kana ‘aqibatu almufsideena
Walaqad atayna dawooda wasulaymana ‘ilman waqala alhamdu lillahi allathee faddalana ‘ala katheerin min ‘ibadihi almu/mineena
Wawaritha sulaymanu dawooda waqala ya ayyuha alnnasu ‘ullimna mantiqa alttayri waooteena min kulli shay-in inna hatha lahuwa alfadlu almubeenu
Wahushira lisulaymana junooduhu mina aljinni waal-insi waalttayri fahum yooza’oona
Hatta itha ataw ‘ala wadi alnnamli qalat namlatun ya ayyuha alnnamlu odkhuloo masakinakum la yahtimannakum sulaymanu wajunooduhu wahum la yash’uroona
Fatabassama dahikan min qawliha waqala rabbi awzi’nee an ashkura ni’mataka allatee an’amta ‘alayya wa’ala walidayya waan a’mala salihan tardahu waadkhilnee birahmatika fee ‘ibadika alssaliheena
Watafaqqada alttayra faqala ma liya la ara alhudhuda am kana mina algha-ibeena
Lao’aththibannahu ‘athaban shadeedan aw laathbahannahu aw laya/tiyannee bisultanin mubeenin
Famakatha ghayra ba’eedin faqala ahattu bima lam tuhit bihi waji/tuka min saba-in binaba-in yaqeenin
Innee wajadtu imraatan tamlikuhum waootiyat min kulli shay-in walaha ‘arshun ‘atheemun
Wajadtuha waqawmaha yasjudoona lilshshamsi min dooni Allahi wazayyana lahumu alshshaytanu a’malahum fasaddahum ‘ani alssabeeli fahum la yahtadoona
Alla yasjudoo lillahi allathee yukhriju alkhabaa fee alssamawati waal-ardi waya’lamu ma tukhfoona wama tu’linoona
Allahu la ilaha illa huwa rabbu al’arshi al’atheemi
Qala sananthuru asadaqta am kunta mina alkathibeena
Ithhab bikitabee hatha faalqih ilayhim thumma tawalla ‘anhum faonthur matha yarji’oona
Qalat ya ayyuha almalao innee olqiya ilayya kitabun kareemun
Innahu min sulaymana wa-innahu 
Alla ta’loo ‘alayya wa/toonee muslimeena
Qalat ya ayyuha almalao aftoonee fee amree ma kuntu qati’atan amran hatta tashhadoona
Qaloo nahnu oloo quwwatin waoloo ba/sin shadeedin waal-amru ilayki faonthuree matha ta/mureena
Qalat inna almulooka itha dakhaloo qaryatan afsadooha waja’aloo a’izzata ahliha athillatan wakathalika yaf’aloona
Wa-innee mursilatun ilayhim bihadiyyatin fanathiratun bima yarji’u almursaloona
Falamma jaa sulaymana qala atumiddoonani bimalin fama ataniya Allahu khayrun mimma atakum bal antum bihadiyyatikum tafrahoona
Irji’ ilayhim falana/tiyannahum bijunoodin la qibala lahum biha walanukhrijannahum minha athillatan wahum saghiroona
Qala ya ayyuha almalao ayyukum ya/teenee bi’arshiha qabla an ya/toonee muslimeena
Qala ‘ifreetun mina aljinni ana ateeka bihi qabla an taqooma min maqamika wa-inne ‘alayhi laqawiyyun ameenun
Qala allathee ‘indahu ‘ilmun mina alkitabi ana ateeka bihi qabla an yartadda ilayka tarfuka falamma raahu mustaqirran ‘indahu qala hatha min fadli rabbee liyabluwanee aashkuru am akfuru waman shakara fa-innama yashkuru linafsihi waman kafara fainna rabbee ghaniyyun kareemun
Qala nakkiroo laha ‘arshaha nanthur atahtadee am takoonu mina allatheena la yahtadoona
Falamma jaat qeela ahakatha ‘arshuki qalat kaannahu huwa waooteena al’ilma min qabliha wakunna muslimeena
Wasaddaha ma kanat ta’budu min dooni Allahi innaha kanat min qawmin kafireena
Qeela laha odkhulee alssarha falamma raat-hu hasibat-hu lujjatan wakashafat ‘an saqayha qala innahu sarhun mumarradun min qawareera qalat rabbi innee thalamtu nafsee waaslamtu ma’a sulaymana lillahi rabbi al’alameena
Walaqad arsalna ila thamooda akhahum salihan ani o’budoo Allaha fa-itha hum fareeqani yakhtasimoona
Qala ya qawmi lima tasta’jiloona bialssayyi-ati qabla alhasanati lawla tastaghfiroona Allaha la’allakum turhamoona
Qaloo ittayyarna bika wabiman ma’aka qala ta-irukum ‘inda Allahi bal antum qawmun tuftanoona
Wakana fee almadeenati tis’atu rahtin yufsidoona fee al-ardi wala yuslihoona
Qaloo taqasamoo biAllahi lanubayyitannahu waahlahu thumma lanaqoolanna liwaliyyihi ma shahidna mahlika ahlihi wa-inna lasadiqoona
Wamakaroo makran wamakarna makran wahum la yash’uroona
Faonthur kayfa kana ‘aqibatu makrihim anna dammarnahum waqawmahum ajma’eena
Fatilka buyootuhum khawiyatan bima thalamoo inna fee thalika laayatan liqawmin ya’lamoona
Waanjayna allatheena amanoo wakanoo yattaqoona
Walootan ith qala liqawmihi ata/toona alfahishata waantum tubsiroona
A-innakum lata/toona alrrijala shahwatan min dooni alnnisa-i bal antum qawmun tajhaloona
Fama kana jawaba qawmihi illa an qaloo akhrijoo ala lootin min qaryatikum innahum onasun yatatahharoona
Faanjaynahu waahlahu illa imraatahu qaddarnaha mina alghabireena
Waamtarna ‘alayhim mataran fasaa mataru almunthareena
Quli alhamdu lillahi wasalamun ‘ala ‘ibadihi allatheena istafa Allahu khayrun amma yushrikoona
Amman khalaqa alssamawati waal-arda waanzala lakum mina alssama-i maan faanbatna bihi hada-iqa thata bahjatin ma kana lakum an tunbitoo shajaraha a-ilahun ma’a Allahi bal hum qawmun ya’diloona
Amman ja’ala al-arda qararan waja’ala khilalaha anharan waja’ala laha rawasiya waja’ala bayna albahrayni hajizan a-ilahun ma’a Allahi bal aktharuhum la ya’lamoona
Amman yujeebu almudtarra itha da’ahu wayakshifu alssoo-a wayaj’alukum khulafaa al-ardi a-ilahun ma’a Allahi qaleelan ma tathakkaroona
Amman yahdeekum fee thulumati albarri waalbahri waman yursilu alrriyaha bushran bayna yaday rahmatihi a-ilahun ma’a Allahi ta’ala Allahu ‘amma yushrikoona
Amman yabdao alkhalqa thumma yu’eeduhu waman yarzuqukum mina alssama-i waal-ardi a-ilahun ma’a Allahi qul hatoo burhanakum in kuntum sadiqeena
Qul la ya’lamu man fee alssamawati waal-ardi alghayba illa Allahu wama yash’uroona ayyana yub’athoona
Bali iddaraka ‘ilmuhum fee al-akhirati bal hum fee shakkin minha bal hum minha ‘amoona
Waqala allatheena kafaroo a-itha kunna turaban waabaona a-inna lamukhrajoona
Laqad wu’idna hatha nahnu waabaona min qablu in hatha illa asateeru alawwaleena
Qul seeroo fee al-ardi faonthuroo kayfa kana ‘aqibatu almujrimeena
Wala tahzan ‘alayhim wala takun fee dayqin mimma yamkuroona
Wayaqooloona mata hatha alwa’du in kuntum sadiqeena
Qul ‘asa an yakoona radifa lakum ba’du allathee tasta’jiloona
Wa-inna rabbaka lathoo fadlin ‘ala alnnasi walakinna aktharahum la yashkuroona
Wa-inna rabbaka laya’lamu ma tukinnu sudooruhum wama yu’linoona
Wama min gha-ibatin fee alssama-i waal-ardi illa fee kitabin mubeenin
Inna hatha alqur-ana yaqussu ‘ala banee isra-eela akthara allathee hum feehi yakhtalifoona
Wa-innahu lahudan warahmatun lilmu/mineena
Inna rabbaka yaqdee baynahum bihukmihi wahuwa al’azeezu al’aleemu
Fatawakkal ‘ala Allahi innaka ‘ala alhaqqi almubeeni
Innaka la tusmi’u almawta wala tusmi’u alssumma alddu’aa itha wallaw mudbireena
Wama anta bihadee al’umyi ‘an dalalatihim in tusmi’u illa man yu/minu bi-ayatina fahum muslimoona
Wa-itha waqa’a alqawlu ‘alayhim akhrajna lahum dabbatan mina al-ardi tukallimuhum anna alnnasa kanoo bi-ayatina la yooqinoona
Wayawma nahshuru min kulli ommatin fawjan mimman yukaththibu bi-ayatina fahum yooza’oona
Hatta itha jaoo qala akaththabtum bi-ayatee walam tuheetoo biha ‘ilman ammatha kuntum ta’maloona
Wawaqa’a alqawlu ‘alayhim bima thalamoo fahum la yantiqoona
Alam yaraw anna ja’alna allayla liyaskunoo feehi waalnnahara mubsiran inna fee thalika laayatin liqawmin yu/minoona
Wayawma yunfakhu fee alssoori fafazi’a man fee alssamawati waman fee al-ardi illa man shaa Allahu wakullun atawhu dakhireena
Watara aljibala tahsabuha jamidatan wahiya tamurru marra alssahabi sun’a Allahi allathee atqana kulla shay-in innahu khabeerun bima taf’aloona
Man jaa bialhasanati falahu khayrun minha wahum min faza’in yawma-ithin aminoona
Waman jaa bialssayyi-ati fakubbat wujoohuhum fee alnnari hal tujzawna illa ma kuntum ta’maloona
Innama omirtu an a’buda rabba hathihi albaldati allathee harramaha walahu kullu shay-in waomirtu an akoona mina almuslimeena
Waan atluwa alqur-ana famani ihtada fa-innama yahtadee linafsihi waman dalla faqul innama ana mina almunthireena
Waquli alhamdu lillahi sayureekum ayatihi fata’rifoonaha wama rabbuka bighafilin ‘amma ta’maloona